Sentencas: In this study, BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-alpha was prepared via a sol-gel combustion method using cerium nitrate, thulium oxide and barium nitrate as raw materials.
Titulo: Characterization and Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performances of BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-α-KCl-NaCl Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: Subsequently, it was reacted with the binary KCl-NaCl salts to obtain BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-alpha-KCl-NaCl composite electrolyte.
Titulo: Characterization and Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performances of BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-α-KCl-NaCl Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The structure, morphology, conductivity and fuel cell performance of the obtained samples were investigated.
Titulo: Characterization and Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performances of BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-α-KCl-NaCl Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: SEM images showed that KCl-NaCl inorganic molten salts covered and filled in the areas between the BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-alpha particles.
Titulo: Characterization and Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performances of BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-α-KCl-NaCl Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The highest power density and conductivity of BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-alpha-KCl-NaCl were 244.4 mW.cm(-2) and 2.1 x 10(-1) S.cm(-1) S.cm(-1) at 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Characterization and Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performances of BaCe0.9Tm0.1O3-α-KCl-NaCl Composite Electrolyte
